rows.label: qst201402_msg0003
rows.name:
If we want to settle this, we really
need to sharpen up our charm skills.

rows.label: qst201402_msg0005
rows.name:
Well, the big showdown's tomorrow.
You better bring your A game!

rows.label: qst201402_msg0006
rows.name:
No fear!
We'll settle this for sure!

rows.label: qst201402_msg0102
rows.name: What's the hot topic right now...?

rows.label: qst201402_msg0103
rows.name:
Two whole hours passed? No way!
I was just having so much fun!

rows.label: qst201402_msg0104
rows.name: Right, so for the next topic...

rows.label: qst201402_msg0105
rows.name:
It's nearly the next day, and we still
haven't run out of things to talk about!

rows.label: qst201402_msg0106
rows.name:
So the thing that everyone's talking
about right now is...

rows.label: qst201402_msg0108
rows.name:
Three o'clock already? Why, I feel as if
I only just got started!

rows.label: qst201402_msg0109
rows.name:
Urgh... This is actually getting kind of
stale. But I can't pull out now...

rows.label: qst201402_msg0110
rows.name:
Ah, it's morning already! And I've got a
real humdinger of a zinger for you
that'll perk you up like hot java! It's...

rows.label: qst201402_msg0111
rows.name:
...ah, it's no good. I'm done. I'm all
talked out.

rows.label: qst201402_msg0201
rows.name: Argh! We need to settle this!

rows.label: qst201402_msg0202
rows.name:
It'd be better to recap from the start,
but I wouldn't want to bore you, so
let's continue from where we left off.
